caption.title: Quantification of PB2-flag expression in 293T cells.
caption.p: The cells were transfected with plasmids expressing the indicated flag-tagged PB2, and cell lysates were analyzed by western blotting using anti-flag antibody. Representative images are shown. Each data point is the mean Â± SD of five independent experiments. NS indicates no statistically significant difference.
